commit.message:
Fix documentation and a ctor in gcov.c

2017-05-02  Martin Liska  <mliska@suse.cz>

	* doc/gcov.texi: Add missing preposition.
	* gcov.c (function_info::function_info): Properly fill up
	all member variables.

From-SVN: r247507
